          "reviewBody": "CPS provides an excellent learning environment with dedicated teachers, well-structured programs, and a focus on both academics and extracurricular activities. The facilities are modern, fostering creativity and growth, while the supportive staff ensures the overall development of students. Highly recommended for quality education and nurturing young minds.",
